{"tid":2077892,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇試過上人住宅工作有艷遇/奇怪經歷??","createTime":"2020-06-24T15:29:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-25T08:31:55.000Z","uid":188406,"like":7,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7b4cb75d091cc9fec0e179cf85dad6f28969a5e5","tid":2077892,"uid":188406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T15:29:54.000Z","msg":"今日有朋友接左單order洗1.5匹冷氣機,<br />\n搵左我做雜工幫手,2個人上人地屋企洗機.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n發生位於藍田某公屋邨的一單位<br />\n一開門就見到位年約30歲既女士,身材似20歲帶點肉肉,目測起碼34D,約高155,樣貌還算可愛甜美,著黑色連身短裙,露出白滑美腿,睇到有少少硬硬地...而且態度又唔差請我地飲可樂<br />\n<br />\n部冷氣機係廳,位置唔錯幾好做,因為冇冷氣,又冇風扇好焗,我同FD都除衫開工,屋企得佢一個,個女人由頭到尾企係旁邊睇住,佢見我地除衫佢又跟住除<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,女人除淨內衣褲睇住我地做,好大壓迫感,我間唔中偷望下佢,佢好似係到陰陰嘴偷笑<br />\n我同FD都怕羞仔冇L用,急急腳拆落黎coil水都唔落,用水槍9射兩射就上番走人.<br />\n<br />\n依加同個FD諗起番都萬般後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家有冇上人地住宅工作既特別經驗分享下? 靈異都得,我知有唔少人遇過"},{"pid":"b56a96b18eceee4f34611cd8cc5989812d906b90","tid":2077892,"uid":2267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T15:49:12.000Z","msg":"一樓一算唔算？"},{"pid":"66c4d7274c0e6e64b865ed6745c661a7f7a9d145","tid":2077892,"uid":110672,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T16:31:22.000Z","msg":"本身尻痕去洗樓，無啦啦有個好唔錯嘅行左出黎<br />\n話跳左制無晒電，好心幫佢整返好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知佢話肚餓叫我幫佢買m記<br />\n我又未食野，咪買兩個餐上去食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個陣都11點，食完再食埋佢<br />\n大家都攰訓左攬住訓天光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一齊行出門口一蚊都無收過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲話幫佢搞掂啲電好man <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我只係俾左m記嘅錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73eb8795fae7f3025d1e04c4f1fe1d0bcfd2c68f","tid":2077892,"uid":349977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T16:33:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5c204a061ed4b75b7032c84921a049076d3daf42","tid":2077892,"uid":110672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73eb8795fae7f3025d1e04c4f1fe1d0bcfd2c68f","tid":2077892,"uid":349977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66c4d7274c0e6e64b865ed6745c661a7f7a9d145","tid":2077892,"uid":110672,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T16:31:22.000Z","msg":"本身尻痕去洗樓，無啦啦有個好唔錯嘅行左出黎<br />\n話跳左制無晒電，好心幫佢整返好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知佢話肚餓叫我幫佢買m記<br />\n我又未食野，咪買兩個餐上去食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個陣都11點，食完再食埋佢<br />\n大家都攰訓左攬住訓天光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一齊行出門口一蚊都無收過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲話幫佢搞掂啲電好man <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我只係俾左m記嘅錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T16:33:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T16:35:44.000Z","msg":"Tst 些份上面"},{"pid":"bb9bbd4a25d074994ac20165ef0c5ee6cdb52977","tid":2077892,"uid":200529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66c4d7274c0e6e64b865ed6745c661a7f7a9d145","tid":2077892,"uid":110672,"like":12,"dislike":0,"sc